19
00:00:44.946 --> 00:00:46.814
JAMESON: <i>There you have it. folks.
Conclusive proof</i>

20
00:00:46.948 --> 00:00:48.950
<i>that Spider-Man was responsible</i>

21
00:00:49.082 --> 00:00:51.218
